LEGO/Scheme
===========
An implementation of Scheme for the Lego MindStorms RCX

Version 0.5.2
Copyright (C) 1999 Adam C. Wick, Mitchell Wagner, Kasey Klipsch
All Rights Reserved.

Archive of Original Website
 â€“ http://web.archive.org/web/20060902030805/http://www.cs.indiana.edu/~mtwagner/legoscheme/


