TO THE TERMS AND CONDITIONS AS EXPRESSED IN THE FILE "LICENSE".


1. System Requirements
----------------------

o Chez Scheme or Petite Chez Scheme Version 6.0 or higher
o Lego MindStorms Robotics Kit
o Visual Basic (included lite version is sufficient)
o Windows ('95, '98, 'NT)
o The Lego MindControl ToolKit


2. Availability
