3. USAGE
--------

To use this product, you must follow the following
steps.

1) Write your Scheme source code.
2) Compile it to Spirit.OCX using LEGO/Scheme 

C:\> petite lego_compiler.ss
<information on usage and copyright notices>
> (lego-compile <Scheme file> <output file>
> (exit)

3) Copy the output file to the mindcontrol directory
4) Load mindcontrol
5) Dump the file into the robot


